title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft updates - Both Dorniers and Junkers receive multiple
description:
This week the an update was released for 4 aircrafts: Dornier Do J Wal, Dornier Do X, Junkers F 13, and Junkers Ju 52.

In this video we will go through the release notes to see what has changed.
Where you will see this update only contains fixes so unfortunately nothing new has been added to these aircrafts. The good thing is that the fixes which are included are more than welcome.
